ription><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3260770/chinese-scientists-claim-find-new-life-old-blood-young?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟更大的自主权如何促进与中国的关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3261128/how-greater-eu-autonomy-can-boost-relations-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>优先考虑“战略自主”将使欧洲能够按照自己的方式与中国接触，并避免受到美国领导地位波动的影响。必须克服欧洲内部分歧、预算限制和地缘政治挑战，以实现新的前进道路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3261128/how-greater-eu-autonomy-can-boost-relations-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着中国大陆的愤怒，台湾和美国进入“更艰难”的贸易谈判阶段</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3261371/taiwan-us-enter-harder-phase-trade-talks-mainland-china-bristles?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士表示，台湾和美国之间的第二阶段贸易谈判已经开始，但随着更多有争议的话题受到关注，进展可能会“更加困难”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3261371/taiwan-us-enter-harder-phase-trade-talks-mainland-china-bristles?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>劳动节假期，随着韩国吸引力减弱，中国游客前往日本和免签目的地</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261360/labour-day-break-chinese-tourists-journey-japan-visa-free-destinations-south-koreas-appeal-wanes?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>日元贬值对于许多中国出境度假者来说太有吸引力了，无法拒绝，而韩国旅游业也受到了打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261360/labour-day-break-chinese-tourists-journey-japan-visa-free-destinations-south-koreas-appeal-wanes?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国嫦娥六号发射升空，执行从月球背面获取第一批岩石样本的任务</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3261346/chinas-change-6-blasts-mission-fetch-first-rock-samples-far-side-moon?